      <title>印度考虑放宽大米出口限制 为全球买家带来利好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/india-mulls-easing-rice-export-limits-in-boon-to-world-buyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，全球最大大米出口国印度可能会放宽对部分品种出口的限制，以避免在10月份新季大米上市前出现供应过剩的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/india-mulls-easing-rice-export-limits-in-boon-to-world-buyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 14:24:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯雷全球资本市场主管林德利由萨维诺接任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/carlyle-global-capital-markets-head-lindley-succeeded-by-savino</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，凯雷集团全球资本市场主管 Brian Lindley 在该另类资产管理公司任职 13 年多后已离职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/carlyle-global-capital-markets-head-lindley-succeeded-by-savino</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 14:16:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利的威尔逊表示，市场回调 10% 的可能性“很高”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-expects-10-market-correction-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利首席美国股票策略师迈克·威尔逊在接受“彭博未平仓合约”采访时表示，企业正在失去定价权，需要降低利率。​​（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-expects-10-market-correction-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 13:53:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度驳斥花旗集团就业报告 称存在数据缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/india-refutes-citigroup-s-employment-report-alleging-data-gaps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府驳斥了花旗集团的一份报告，该报告称即使印度经济以每年 7% 的速度增长，该国也将难以创造足够的就业机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/india-refutes-citigroup-s-employment-report-alleging-data-gaps</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 13:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利的威尔逊表示，市场目前“陷入困境”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-says-markets-stuck-right-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利首席美国股票策略师迈克·威尔逊在接受“彭博未平仓合约”采访时表示，市场陷入了一种难以挑选股票、难以超越的环境中。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-says-markets-stuck-right-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 13:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>策略师表示股市上涨需要美国财报季的强劲表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/a-bumper-us-earnings-season-is-key-for-stocks-to-scale-new-highs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些华尔街策略师表示，美国企业需要在季度财报季中实现强劲增长，才能延续美国股市破纪录的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/a-bumper-us-earnings-season-is-key-for-stocks-to-scale-new-highs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织将考虑降低大额借款人罚款的方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/imf-to-discuss-options-for-lowering-penalties-on-big-borrowers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一些国家担心由于利率上升导致成本变得不合理之后，国际货币基金组织将讨论对其向最大借款人收取的费用进行审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/imf-to-discuss-options-for-lowering-penalties-on-big-borrowers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 08:42:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风风险抵消供应平衡，欧洲天然气价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/european-gas-prices-rise-as-hurricane-beryl-heads-toward-texas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商评估了欧洲地区稳健的库存，以抵御主要燃料供应地德克萨斯州遭受的飓风影响，欧洲天然气价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/european-gas-prices-rise-as-hurricane-beryl-heads-toward-texas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:31:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电凭借人工智能的持续发展，市值突破 1 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/tsmc-shares-soar-to-record-as-hunger-marketing-seen-working</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在摩根士丹利和其他券商在台湾半导体制造股份有限公司公布业绩前上调其目标价后，该公司市值一度突破 1 万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/tsmc-shares-soar-to-record-as-hunger-marketing-seen-working</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 04:11:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风贝丽尔对德克萨斯州运营的风险减弱，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于飓风贝丽尔不太可能对德克萨斯州的原油基础设施造成重大破坏，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-8</guid>
